org.jnosql.diana.api.column.query

Interface ColumnQueryBuild

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ColumnFrom, ColumnLimit, ColumnNameOrder, ColumnSkip, ColumnWhere

    public interface ColumnQueryBuild
    The last step to the build of ColumnQuery. It either can return a new ColumnQuery instance or execute a query with ColumnFamilyManager and ColumnFamilyManagerAsync
